title: Jasmine Thompson - Bundle of Tantrums
description: In July 2013 Jasmine Thompson released a cover of Naughty Boy's single "La la La". In August she released a cover of Taylor Swift's single "Everything Has Changed" as a duet with Gerald Ko, a cover of Passenger's single "Let Her Go" and a cover of David Guetta's single "Titanium". In September 2013 she released her debut album Bundle of Tantrums which included the singles "La la La", "Let Her Go" and "Titanium"
